comment._content: This row of buildings is featured in one of the plague album pictures, but several years earlier than this photo. Several businesses have changed, the Caledonian Hotel at left has a new awning, and the cable tram has been replaced by electricity as well as turning the corner to finish at Erskine Street. So about 1905-1910? Plague Album No.1, no.55 - acms.sl.nsw.gov.au/album/ItemViewer.aspx?itemid=823637&am...
